        <p class="text-sm text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400">P is worth 3 points. Placing PRE- so P lands on DLS gives 6 from one tile. Always aim for premium square alignment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-300 mb-1">Extend board words</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400">If HEAT, WASH, or JUDGE appear, prepending PRE creates valid words. PRE- works with more roots than most players realise.</p>
      </div>
