      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 mb-2">Enter your tiles and find every PRE- word instantly</p>
      <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors">Open Word Finder →</a>
